data.content:
Danh từ
(cách viết khác Commonwealth of Nations) khối cộng đồng
the Commonwealth of Australia
khối cộng đồng Australia
the Commonwealth
(số ít)
Khối liên hiệp thịnh vượng chung

noun
plural -wealths
[count] :a group of countries or states that have political or economic connections with one another - often + of
a commonwealth of states
a the Commonwealth :a U.S. state - used officially of Kentucky, Massachusetts, Pennsylvania, and Virginia
the Commonwealth of Kentucky
[count] :a political unit that is like a U.S. state but that pays no federal taxes and has only a representative in Congress who does not vote - used officially of Puerto Rico and of the Northern Mariana Islands;
the Commonwealth :the countries that were once part of the British Empire
